# jodi text shadow dite chai (source code pen => https://codepen.io/Sablu-Hasan-the-lessful/pen/wBWzdJb)
h1{
  color:white;
  text-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan,
               0 0 20px cyan,
               0 0 30px cyan,
               0 0 40px cyan
}


